entries.journal_entry_description: Boba Fett has employed you. It's usually a good idea to do what he suggests. People that don't play their cards right against Fett have a habit of catching a case of death.
entries.journal_entry_title: Working for Boba Fett, phase I
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The package Fett wants you to deliver to his contact in the Restuss refugee camp star port is a piece of cloth that has a ring inside, with a finger still attached to it.
